{
  "text": "Equation (15) is consistent with the condition introduced in [CITATION_1] , but here we provide a condition that is based on a more accurate estimate of the maximum eigenvalue of A 0 . We can rewrite Eq. (15) in terms of the vacuum wavelength λ 0 as",
